{"title":"PD虚拟机安装win7开机动画消失解决","uid":"bb99acdccd6c5fc34736f2abf04e3f25","slug":"PD虚拟机安装win7开机动画消失解决","date":"2021-11-06T04:07:53.000Z","updated":"2021-11-09T05:14:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/PD虚拟机安装win7开机动画消失解决.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://gitee.com/dmnb/blogfiles/raw/master/images/img0.jpg","content":"<p>上大学了嘛，每天 PPT 不重样的，啥课都得来个 PPT。有一个课的教室 Office 版本为 2010，身为 PPT 卷王，为了实现炫酷的动画，直接装了个 win7 + office 2010。很快啊，我就发现这虚拟机里 win7 的开机动画没有了，变成 vista 那样的绿条条，就挺丑的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/11/06/ViKR7Qn49JqXxAa.png\"></p>\n<p>然后就在 Parallels 的论坛里找到了解决方法。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://forum.parallels.com/threads/windows-7-boot-faster-and-changed-logo.272301/\">呐</a></p>\n<p>使用管理员权限运行 cmd，修改 BCD 文件中 <code>graphicsmodedisabled</code>的值即可。</p>\n<p>当<code>graphicsmodedisabled</code>为<code>Yes</code>时，显示 vista 开机动画：</p>\n<p><code>bcdedit /set graphicsmodedisabled Yes</code></p>\n<p>当<code>graphicsmodedisabled</code>为<code>No</code>时，显示 win7 开机动画：</p>\n<p><code>bcdedit /set graphicsmodedisabled No</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/dmnb/blogfiles/raw/master/images/image-20211106123013308.png\"></p>\n","text":"上大学了嘛，每天 PPT 不重样的，啥课都得来个 PPT。有一个课的教室 Office 版本为 2010，身为 PPT 卷王，为了实现炫酷的动画，直接装了个 win7 + office 2010。很快啊，我就发现这虚拟机里 win7 的开机动画没有了，变成 vista 那样的绿条...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":388,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"PD","slug":"PD","count":1,"path":"api/tags/PD.json"},{"name":"Parallels","slug":"Parallels","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Parallels.json"},{"name":"win7","slug":"win7","count":1,"path":"api/tags/win7.json"},{"name":"虚拟机","slug":"虚拟机","count":1,"path":"api/tags/虚拟机.json"},{"name":"开机动画","slug":"开机动画","count":1,"path":"api/tags/开机动画.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Mai","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://dmnb.me/images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"野蛮生长砖家","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"